    "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" lang=\"en\" xml:lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\" />\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"nofollow\" />\n<title>Group5 - Threat Group Cards: A Threat Actor Encyclopedia</title>\n<link href=\"/style.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" />\n</head>\n<body class=\"mbody\">\n<div class=\"logos\">\n<table border=\"0\"><tr><td><a href=\"https://www.etda.or.th\"><img src=\"/img/logo-etda.png\" height=\"50\" alt=\"ETDA\" title=\"Visit the ETDA website\" /></a></td>\n<td><font size=\"3\">สำนักงานพัฒนาธุรกรรมทางอิเล็กทรอนิกส์<br />Electronic Transactions Development Agency</font></td></tr></table>\n</div>\n<link href=\"/menubar.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" />\n<div id=\"menubar\">\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi\">Groups</a>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listtools.cgi\">Tools</a>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"/cgi-bin/aptsearch.cgi\">Search</a>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"/cgi-bin/aptstats.cgi\">Statistics</a>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"graph\">\n<div class=\"gline\"><img src=\"/img/clear.gif\" width=\"1\" height=\"3\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n<div><img src=\"/img/report.jpg\" width=\"900\" alt=\"Report\" /></div>\n<a name=\"top\"></a>\n<div class=\"searchdiv\"><a href=\"/cgi-bin/aptsearch.cgi\" title=\"Search the database\" class=\"inlink\">Search</a></div>\n<div class=\"outermain\"><a href=\"/cgi-bin/aptgroups.cgi\" class=\"inlink\" title=\"Home\">Home</a> &gt; <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi\" class=\"inlink\" title=\"List all groups\">List all groups</a> &gt; Group5</div>\n<h1>Threat Group Cards: A Threat Actor Encyclopedia</h1>\n<div class=\"innermainov\">\n<h3><a href=\"/cgi-bin/showcard.cgi?u=316b9d45-f67a-4595-bdf3-5137489fb3c5\" title=\"Get permanent link to this card\" class=\"inlink\"><img src=\"/img/link.png\" height=\"16\" alt=\"Permanent link\" /></a> APT group: Group5</h3>\n<table width=\"100%\" class=\"tborder\">\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Names</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">Group5 <i><font size=\"-2\">",
    "</font></i><br />G0043 <i><font size=\"-2\">",
    "</font></i></td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Country</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\"><a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?c=Iran\" title=\"Search for all threat groups from Iran\" class=\"inlink\"><img src=\"/img/flags/Iran.png\" alt=\"Iran\" width=\"33\" height=\"20\" /> Iran</a></td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Sponsor</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">State-sponsored</td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Motivation</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\"><a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?m=Information%20theft%20and%20espionage\" title=\"Search for all threat groups with motivation Information theft and espionage\" class=\"inlink\">Information theft and espionage</a></td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">First seen</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">2015</td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Description</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">",
    "A threat actor using Iranian-language tools, Iranian hosting companies, operating from the Iranian IP space at times was observed targeting the Syrian opposition in an elaborately staged malware operation, Citizen Lab researchers reveal.<br /><br />The operation was first noticed in late 2015, when a member of the Syrian opposition flagged a suspicious email containing a PowerPoint slideshow, which led researchers to a watering hole website with malicious programs, malicious PowerPoint files, and Android malware.<br /><br />The threat actor was targeting Windows and Android devices of well-connected individuals in the Syrian opposition, researchers discovered. They called the actor Group5, because it targets Syrian opposition after regime-linked malware groups, the <a href=\"/cgi-bin/showcard.cgi?g=Syrian%20Electronic%20Army%20%28SEA%29%2C%20Deadeye%20Jackal\" title=\"Show the card for Syrian Electronic Army",
    ", Deadeye Jackal\" class=\"inlink\">Syrian Electronic Army",
    ", Deadeye Jackal</a>, ISIS",
    ", and a group linked to Lebanon did the same in the past.</td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Observed</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">Countries: <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?v=Syria\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that target Syria\" class=\"inlink\">Syria</a>.</td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Tools used</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\"><a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?t=DroidJack\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that use DroidJack\" class=\"inlink\">DroidJack</a>, <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?t=NanoCore%20RAT\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that use NanoCore RAT\" class=\"inlink\">NanoCore RAT</a>, <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?t=njRAT\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that use njRAT\" class=\"inlink\">njRAT</a>.</td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Information</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">&lt;<a href=\"https://www.securityweek.com/iranian-actor-group5-targeting-syrian-opposition\" title=\"Follow external link\" class=\"exlink\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.securityweek.com/iranian-actor-group5-targeting-syrian-opposition</a>&gt;</td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">MITRE ATT&amp;CK</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">&lt;<a href=\"https://attack.mitre.org/groups/G0043/\" title=\"Follow external link\" class=\"exlink\" target=\"_blank\">https://attack.mitre.org/groups/G0043/</a>&gt;</td></tr>\n</table>\n<p>Last change to this card: 16 August 2025</p>\n<p>Download this actor card in <a href=\"/cgi-bin/getcard.cgi?g=Group5&o=p\" title=\"Download this card in PDF format\" class=\"inlink\">PDF</a> or <a href=\"/cgi-bin/getcard.cgi?g=Group5&o=j\" title=\"Download this card in JSON format\" class=\"inlink\">JSON</a> format</p>\n<div class=\"backtotop\"><a href=\"#top\" title=\"Back to the top\" class=\"inlink\">&uarr;</a></div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\">\n<tr><td width=\"80%\" rowspan=\"4\" valign=\"top\">\n<p>Infrastructure and Security Department<br />\nElectronic Transactions Development Agency</p>\n<h3>Follow us on</h3>\n<a href=\"https://facebook.com/ETDA.Thailand\"><img src=\"/img/icon-facebook.png\" alt=\"Facebook\" title=\"Follow us on Facebook\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/etda_thailand\"><img src=\"/img/icon-twitter.png\" alt=\"Twitter\" title=\"Follow us on Twitter\" /></a>\n</td><td colspan=\"2\">\n<h3>Report incidents</h3>\n</td>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"0%\"><img src=\"/img/icon-phone.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" alt=\"Telephone\" title=\"Telephone\" /></td>\n<td width=\"20%\"><strong>+66"
